OL,3,CInquiry into abuse at Muckamore to
OL,4,Cpublish its findings
OL,6,FA public inquiry examining allegations
OL,7,Fof the abuse of vulnerable patients at
OL,8,FMuckamore Abbey Hospital is to publish
OL,9,Fits report on Thursday.
OL,11,FMuckamore Abbey, run by the Belfast
OL,12,FHealth and Social Care Trust, was a
OL,13,Fhospital in Co Antrim for adults with
OL,14,Fsevere learning disabilities and
OL,15,Fmental health needs.
OL,17,FThe inquiry examined allegations of
OL,18,Fabuse of patients at the facility.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
