PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781790495
OL,3,CInquiry into abuse at Muckamore to
OL,4,Cpublish its findings
OL,6,FGlynn Brown, whose son Aaron had been
OL,7,Fa patient at the hospital and who
OL,8,Fpreviously raised the alarm about the
OL,9,Ffacility, was among those who attended
OL,10,Fthe inquiry.
OL,12,FGroups including the Society of
OL,13,FParents and Friends of Muckamore Abbey
OL,14,Fand Action For Muckamore, as well as
OL,15,Fthe department of health, Belfast
OL,16,FHealth Trust, the Regulation and
OL,17,FQuality Improvement Authority and the
OL,18,Fpolice, gave statements to the inquiry.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
