PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781790495
OL,3,CInquiry into abuse at Muckamore to
OL,4,Cpublish its findings
OL,6,FChairman Tom Kark KC said it was
OL,7,F"highly unusual" for a public inquiry
OL,8,Fto take place simultaneously with a
OL,9,Flarge police investigation and
OL,10,Fcriminal trial proceedings.
OL,12,FA memorandum of understanding (MoU)
OL,13,Fwas entered with the police and the
OL,14,FPublic Prosecution Service in Northern
OL,15,FIreland to ensure the inquiry did not
OL,16,Finterfere with the criminal
OL,17,Fproceedings.
OL,19,FThe inquiry is expected to have
OL,20,Fsubmitted its final report to Health
OL,21,FMinister Mike Nesbitt.
