OL,3,CInquiry into abuse at Muckamore to
OL,4,Cpublish its findings
OL,6,FThe hospital, which first opened in
OL,7,F1949, was due to close in June 2024
OL,8,Fbut this was delayed as some patients
OL,9,Fhad not found alternative
OL,10,Faccommodation.
